title: Bucks Win Game 5 to Take a 3-2 Series Lead | Postgame
description:
Immediately following Game 5, KOC and J. Kyle Mann get together to discuss another exciting Bucks win. They start with Jrue Holiday's impressive performance (1:30), then they discuss the evolution of Giannis (12:00) and if the Suns will be able to force a Game 7 (22:45). Plus, have the Finals taught us anything about how teams should approach the draft (29:00)?
Hosts: Kevin O'Connor and J. Kyle Mann
Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
